antsrRegsitration

antsrRegistration.Rd

C++ type used to represent an ITK image registration filter

# S4 method for antsrRegistration
show(object)

Arguments

object

input object to convert

Slots

dimension

usually 2 or 3 but can be 4

precision

math precision is float or double'

components

number of components in image

pixeltype

pixeltype of images

smoothing

smoothing for each level

transform

type of transform

optimizer

optimizer type to use

interpolator

interpolator type to use

sampling

sampling type for image-to-image metric

metric

image-to-image metric for registration

iterations

max iterations at each level

shrink

shrink factor for each level

samplingStrategy

type of metric sampling

convergence

metric convergence value

smoothingPhysical

flag indicating smoothing values are in mm (default in in voxels)

nLevels

number of levels in registration
